description:
Blood Sugar Master is a lightweight blood sugar recording APP with AI Health. Products designed specifically for smartphones will help you better manage diabetes and keep it under control. Through the AI intelligent system, you can choose the evolution of blood sugar trends to track your health status.

We will also provide you with the ability to share your blood sugar knowledge. Our app only provides the function of recording blood sugar and cannot detect blood sugar. If you need to test your blood sugar, please use professional medical equipment.

The current version brings:
- Basic blood sugar tracking by event type (before breakfast, before dinner, after lunch, etc.);
- Filter by historical event type/tag;
- Labeling (exercises for tracking reactions, food types, etc.);
- Use and set different blood glucose level units - mg/dl or mmol/l;
- Through the AI Health system, analyze your recent blood sugar levels and give health suggestions;

Whether you have diabetes or just want to monitor your blood sugar levels, this app is for you.
-User friendly interface
- Easy to use features
- Detailed charts and statistics

Disclaimer: This application is only used for numerical recording and reference. The suggestions given by AI Health are for reference only and cannot be used as a basis for pathological diagnosis.

Source of diabetes-related information: https://medlineplus.gov/diabetes.html
